A. Fedynitch 12.02.2016

The C-Port of the NRLMSISE-00 model by DOMINIK BORODOWSKI is
redistributed here in unmodified form. Please refer to the
"DOCUMENTATION" document for all related info and authorship
information. All rights remain at the author.


The ctypes interface (ONLY *.py files) is written by A. Fedynitch 
and is licensed under the same MIT License conditions as the MCEq 
package. Refer to the LICENSE text at the bottom of this document.

Instructions:

1) cd c-NRLMSISE-00
2) make
3) change in mceq_config.py "msis_python" variable to "ctypes"
4) Enjoy the massive speed-up for atmospheric calculations  





